purpose: To offer developers a source of customizable generative AI code snippets for seamless integration into their applications.
principle: Utilizes generative AI frameworks and libraries to provide pre-built code snippets that can be easily adapted and integrated into various applications.

limitations: Limited to the provided code snippets; users may need to adjust or extend snippets for specific use cases.
